text: Dhanial is one of the largest Chander-Vanshi/Yadu-Vanshi Khastriya Rajput tribe living in Potohar plateau and Lower Himalayas for the last eight centuries Most of the Dhanials are settled in the cities of Rawalpindi, Islamabad and in Kotli Sattian and Murree Hills and Ponch area of Kashmir. == References == Category:Ethnic groups in Pakistan Category:Tribes of Pakistan Category:Punjabi people
title: Dhanial
